            <div class="block w-full px-4 py-2 text-black no-underline hover:bg-gray-200 border-b border-gray-300">Cirque du Soleil CRYSTAL</div>
            <div class="block w-full px-4 py-2 text-black no-underline hover:bg-gray-200 border-b border-gray-300">Drawn to Life</div>
